    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><i>九石迷阵将你吞噬，</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你已困于九石迷阵之中，这是一个活体结构，其中的无尽秘密就在眼前静待发掘。万物皆可任你移动、旋转与毁灭。运用这无上之力，前往那些曾遥不可及之境吧！筑起桥梁，挖通隧道、另辟蹊径，去揭示这世间九重天地的秘密！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203340/extras/741691457168541ecfda4b7f8cd8f3fe.poster.avif?t=1765314623\" width=1170 height=440 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203340/extras/741691457168541ecfda4b7f8cd8f3fe.webm?t=1765314623\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203340/extras/741691457168541ecfda4b7f8cd8f3fe.mp4?t=1765314623\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >逃离九石迷阵</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >唯有通晓万千真理，迷阵之壁才会为你退散。破解谜题，去发掘那些足以重新定义从古至今所有“可能”的惊人法门。万事万物皆触手可及，但前提是，成为此方世界的主宰。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203340/extras/b31120320c7c63d9d010075d54accf89.poster.avif?t=1765314623\" width=1170 height=440 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203340/extras/b31120320c7c63d9d010075d54accf89.webm?t=1765314623\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203340/extras/b31120320c7c63d9d010075d54accf89.mp4?t=1765314623\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >驾驭九石迷阵</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >对于最无畏的冒险者而言，逃脱仅是开端。当你登峰造极之时，九石迷阵自当臣服于你的意志之下。无上之力，静待那寥寥敢于问鼎终极之人。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >游戏特点</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >精炼体验，探索九大世界</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >创意解密，自由实验，享受醍醐灌顶的时刻</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无需解锁，自由发掘那扇始终为你敞开的妙法之门</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >自辟蹊径，以你独有的方式探索并逃离九石迷阵</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >穷尽九石迷阵的奥秘，你的每一丝努力都将得到回报</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >由Clockmaker倾情打造的萦绕于心的氛围原声</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203340/extras/ddd08e44c816a6745e9135ac0854e04c.poster.avif?t=1765314623\" width=576 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203340/extras/ddd08e44c816a6745e9135ac0854e04c.webm?t=1765314623\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3203340/extras/ddd08e44c816a6745e9135ac0854e04c.mp4?t=1765314623\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
